Lower Costs: Gas fees on Base are a fraction of Ethereum mainnet’s, enabling more frequent contract interactions and lower costs for users.
Faster Transactions: Base’s Optimistic Rollup architecture ensures quicker transaction confirmations, improving user experience.
Seamless Integration: Developers can reuse Ethereum smart contracts, libraries, and tools without modification.
Growing Ecosystem: Base’s association with Coinbase attracts a wide user base, increasing the potential reach of your dApp.
Scalable Infrastructure: Base supports high-throughput applications, making it suitable for DeFi, NFTs, gaming, and more.
Community and Support: Base’s integration with the OP Stack and Coinbase’s resources provides robust documentation and developer support.

